1. Molim vas da napravimo *pauzu* od 15 minuta. (Please let's take a *break* for 15 minutes.)
2. Nema *pauze* dok se posao ne završi. (There's no *pause* until the job is finished.)
3. Dali su nam *pauzu* od sat vremena za ručak. (They gave us a *break* of one hour for lunch.)
4. Moramo napraviti *pauzu* u vezi s tim projektom. (We need to take a *break* regarding that project.)
5. Ovo je *pauza* u mom životu. (This is a *break* in my life.)
6. Nikada ne zaboravite da napravite *pauzu* tokom rada. (Never forget to take a *break* during work.)
7. Bio je prisiljen da napravi *pauzu* u svojoj karijeri. (He was forced to take a *break* in his career.)
8. Zašto ne bi napravili *pauzu* i popili kafu zajedno? (Why don't we take a *break* and have coffee together?)
9. Nakon dugog puta, odlučili su da naprave *pauzu* i odmore se. (After a long journey, they decided to take a *break* and rest.)
10. Kada radite od kuće, važno je napraviti *pauzu* za vežbanje. (When you work from home, it's important to take a *break* for exercise.)